name: Luke's Backpack
Lore: 'Made on Dantooine. Luke used the many pockets in his gundark-skin backpack to carry supplies while on patrol.',
Text: 'Deploy on any character. May carry and use any number of devices. May also carry Yoda, Kabe or any one Jawa or Ewok (as if riding a creature vehicle). Adds 1 to training destiny when carrying the Mentor.',
